"<strong>\n"
"                                                    We kick off our courses "
"on the first Monday of every month, providing you with all the knowledge "
"needed to dive into the vast ocean.&amp;nbsp;<br/>\n"
"                                                    The courses span from "
"Monday to Friday and include insurance, equipment rental, and exam fees.\n"
"                                                </strong>\n"
"                                                <br/>"
